In the Bible, peace is not a passive word. Its an active word. It doesnt only mean the absence of something, but the existence of something. Thats what Jesus meant when He said, Blessed are the peacemakers. Watch the clip below and find out about thekind of peace that gives lasting happiness and about the One who can give it to you and your family.
